{"tid":2450363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2名學生認於旺角堵路 官指有悔意延至月底判刑候索報告","createTime":"2021-03-17T10:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T13:08:59.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c15ab7766ff26ee43b333998d5b50eee7e0bd24","tid":2450363,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:26:38.000Z","msg":"去年5月27日，有示威者於旺角登打士街一帶聚集反對港區國安法，17歲中六男生及19歲浸大女生在旺角一帶馬路擺放膠籃及摺枱等雜物，早前承認一項公眾地方造成阻礙罪。裁判官<span class=\"red\">鄭念慈不接納被告行為對交通影響輕微，形容是典型的堵路行為</span>，考慮到二人坦白認罪，有悔意，將索取<span class=\"red\">社會服務令及感化報告</span>，案件後至本月31日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n被告為17歲劉姓中六男生及19歲浸大女生李 ，二人於去年5月27日下午2時許在旺角登打士街35號外馬路中心，放下兩個膠籃和一張槢枱，導致一輛輕型貨車被阻，當場被捕。"},{"pid":"e8eea388538bb5b138a9dec37ba8d133725e0970","tid":2450363,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5fac10b6b4d9b5d5abdfc7c2339801f7199b84","tid":2450363,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d458473c0bd9fe1ee60c82779a34313aff2c0f6","tid":2450363,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"裁判官鄭念慈不接納辯方指，被告行為對交通的影響輕微，形容是典型堵路行為，考慮到兩人坦白認罪，將索取感化及社會服務令報告，但強調仍開放所有判刑選項。裁判官將案件押後至 3 月 31 日判刑，期間兩人以原有條件保釋。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E9%98%BB%E7%A4%99-%E5%AE%98%E7%B4%A2%E5%8F%96%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%A4%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%25A4%2599-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=92141afa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%25A4%2599-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&h=ba51d484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%85%A9%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E9%98%BB%E7%A4%99-%E5%AE%98%E7%B4%A2%E5%8F%96%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%A4%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4/</a>"},{"pid":"5e8eb58f1bcad4958b87bc6f6e314ac8c67f1c63","tid":2450363,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"期間兩人以原有條件保釋<br />\n<br />\n好在唔洗還押<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4141c24cd246d84a130e36329cb3a6bb28eb506","tid":2450363,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:09:33.000Z","msg":"鄭念慈=支那狗"},{"pid":"b9dc0072e52afb2aec8cc5dd3afc138fdfead73a","tid":2450363,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:08:59.000Z","msg":"去年5月27日有市民發起反對國歌法示威，警方當日拘捕逾百人。事隔半年，兩名學生被指在旺角用膠籃、摺枱，或站在馬路上堵路，被控在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，兩人今日在九龍城裁判法院承認控罪，裁判官鄭念慈下令先索取感化及社會服務令報告再作判刑，<span class=\"red\">明言不排除判處監禁，其間准許二人繼續保釋候判。</span><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/7N5L6TZECRCH5LAB2S5YO6IGQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2F7N5L6TZECRCH5LAB2S5YO6IGQU%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=0cfbfdab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2F7N5L6TZECRCH5LAB2S5YO6IGQU%2F&h=0d84c1c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/7N5L6TZECRCH5LAB2S5YO6IGQU/</a>"}]}